text: BibractellaStorozhenko S (2002) Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie 81(3): 600. is a monotypic genus of grasshoppers in the subfamily Catantopinae and tribe Gereniini. The single species Bibractella sugonjaevi has only been recorded from Vietnam to date.Orthoptera Species File (Version 5.0/5.0: retrieved 5 September 2019) == References == == External links == * Category:Acrididae genera Category:Catantopinae Category:Orthoptera of Indo-China Category:Monotypic insect genera
